91
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:09,450
You're still one step away from becoming an immortal.

92
00:06:09,790 --> 00:06:11,990
When the morning bell rings tomorrow,

93
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:12,830
the Flower God's Mansion

94
00:06:13,030 --> 00:06:14,390
will send someone down to the mortal world

95
00:06:14,530 --> 00:06:16,000
to bestow the flower fairy's token upon you.

96
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,350
Qingcheng.

97
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,160
