104
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,070
Right?

105
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:35,040
Yes, yes, yes.

106
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,720
Dragon feathers, dragon feathers.

107
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,390
Cheers!

108
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,270
