126
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:40,950
I've always been by your side,

127
00:07:42,130 --> 00:07:43,159
I've never left you.

128
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,070
Master.

129
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:53,720
I miss you so much.

130
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:56,800
I really

131
00:07:59,090 --> 00:08:00,200
miss you so much.

132
00:08:03,110 --> 00:08:05,260
The morning bell has just rung.

133
00:08:05,660 --> 00:08:07,220
