134
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:15,950
Which one of you is Gu Qingcheng?

135
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,680
This is Fairy Nanxing.

136
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,120
With her position

137
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,600
