138
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,680
she's so arrogant.

139
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,870
I'm asking which one of you is Gu Qingcheng.

140
00:08:27,210 --> 00:08:28,520
[Fairy Nanxing, Celestial Attendant in the Heavenly Realm]

141
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:30,870
Stop putting on airs!

142
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:31,630
There are only two people here.

143
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:32,720
