144
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,030
Can't you tell which of us is Gu Qingcheng?

145
00:08:34,049 --> 00:08:35,960
Immortals in the lower realm are indeed noisy.

146
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,840
