147
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:38,720
You...

148
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:39,240
Longque, Longque.

149
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,909
Now it's not the time to argue.

150
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:46,870
I'm Gu Qingcheng.

151
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,240
Greetings, Fairy.

152
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:49,550
