269
00:15:07,410 --> 00:15:09,080
Burn it after you read it.

270
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,900
Immortal Yuxiao.

271
00:15:24,750 --> 00:15:25,750
Why are you here?

272
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:31,960
Back then, Senior Jiang Li

273
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,670
