279
00:15:44,910 --> 00:15:46,360
collected by Flower Goddess Jiang Li.

280
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:52,080
Is it true that

281
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:54,480
there are only classic books here?

282
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:05,790
Yes.

283
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,510
What else do you think

284
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,670
there should be, Your Excellency?

